Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.69,0:00:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.32,0:00:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, when you were brought into my hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.37,0:00:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,your name was Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.83,0:00:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And your brother's name was Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.93,0:00:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fortner!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer! Mr. Maurer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fortner! It's Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.26,0:02:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna... I mean,\NI've brought Nina home safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call the police from here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't look like\Nthe police ever came...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:02:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can't be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Live...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... Come back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You must come back to life!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Your favorite cigarettes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I... killed... him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed him... I killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But that day, I killed my brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I brought him back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The phone line has been cut...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to get\Naway from here quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll come to take you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the police.\NWe received a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind,\Nwe'll have a look around inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you two all right? Any injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank heavens.\NWe'll have help soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll take care of the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll hear your stories\Ndown at headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she the victims' daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So that means\Nyou didn't see who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To think something like that could\Nhappen in such a peaceful town...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you from? China?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm Japanese.\NMy name is Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're Japanese...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What a terrible experience for you\Nin such a faraway land...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Steady...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Heidelberg Police Department\Nis in the middle of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We're from Mannheim Precinct\Nin the next town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder why they're taking us\Nto the next precinct...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be there in about 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He said they got a call...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They came because they got a call...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who could have called them?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The phone line was dead...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This car came without sirens blaring...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Would the police whisk away the people who{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}discovered the bodies without first securing the scene?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still, those police IDs\Nlooked authentic...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Blood!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It couldn't be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that these men...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A roadblock?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:09:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank goodness...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're searching for a hit-and-run driver, so we'd appreciate your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Detective Mesner\Nand Detective Muller.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... See you're doing your job...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you on your way\Nback to headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you've got a new car. How nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:17.85,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a junk heap in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's 'cause you don't take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl says she doesn't feel well.\NCan we go out and get some air?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Did those two do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are they really detectives?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But what about that blood?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whose call did they receive?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They didn't even turn on their siren...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should we do? What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything all right, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave you my name,\Nbut I didn't tell you that I was a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a grocery story nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I even found some clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.10,0:12:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's bread, sausage and cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I even had them pour\Nsome coffee into this thermos...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You may not have any appetite,\Nbut you've got to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you'd better change your clothes. You're freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There were lots of dead people...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother and I walked among them,\Njust the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like... we were the only people\Nleft in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was that?\NCan't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We crossed the border...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A man and and his wife cheered us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They were so kind to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.88,0:13:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then my brother said that\Nhe had a good plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not long after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The man and his wife died...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but everyone who's ever been nice to us... all die...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:14:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But one day, I discovered the reason why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That rainy day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about\NMr. and Mrs. Liebert, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother shot them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother killed them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's killed them all up till now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I took the gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I aimed it at my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He laughed as he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"After you shoot me, throw the gun outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure you shoot me in the head."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I shot him like he said...\NI aimed for his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't saved him,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,my mom and dad\Nwouldn't have been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move from this place.\NI'll go to the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the detectives last night\Nwere the real thing, that means that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,someone in the police department\Nis on Johan's side...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't just stay here like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, listen, Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan is trying to take you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to hide\Nif someone comes looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to eat, drink some hot coffee, then sleep for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how people go on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You must think about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your future...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't you have any leads?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Is there any connection to the string of killings of middle-age couples throughout Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, we are putting all of\Nour resources into this case,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but I am not free to disclose any details.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We have found that\NMr. and Mrs. Fortner have a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That is under investigation as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was that newspaper reporter,\NMaurer, with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that Japanese guy\Nwho is said to have been with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese? He sounds suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that murder at Heidelberg Castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.78,0:16:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,that occurred at nearly the same time,\Nthe work of the same killer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Heidelberg Castle...?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So he was killed, as well?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we will keep you\Nabreast of the happenings!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me... Please let me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I appreciate the help offered\Nby the Mannheim police,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Detectives Mesner and Muller.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give us our orders.\NWe'll do all we can to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How are the investigations\Ncoming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We can talk about it inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're real...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those guys are really\Nwith the police...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Heidelberg Post!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I can't hear you!\NThe editing room is in chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:18:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.52,0:18:01.48,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,We have to find that Japanese guy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:03.52,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,who was with Maurer! He knows something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please quiet down! I'm on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I will bring an important witness\Nto your office at 5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not let the police know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?!\NThis isn't a hoax, is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can't trust the police,\Nthere's only the paper...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that can... keep Nina safe...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be in here\Nwithout permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.31,0:18:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you're here from\Nthe federal police to investigate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the killings of the middle-age couples,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We only have files on\Nthe killing at the castle here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... Something was bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The case you're looking at and\Nthis one happened at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be the same perpetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.92,0:19:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy... It looks like there are signs\Nthat his hands had been tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find rope or anything nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No... It had been removed\Nby the time the victim was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I... see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are four possible routes\Nof escape from the scene...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He had to consider whether\Nhe'd be hidden from sight,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}how crowded the area was\Nwhere he'd come out,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the locations of the lights.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, it's me... It's Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina! You needn't hide anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!! Nina!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina... Was she taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have left her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dr. Tenma, it wasn't your fault.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You just did what you\Nhad to do as a doctor...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It wasn't your fault.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please eat the sandwiches\Nand get some rest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.36,0:21:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want you to survive,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and save as many people as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.24,0:21:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nina Fortner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.09,0:22:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nina... What do you intend to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.60,0:22:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you intend to try to\Nkill him again?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.81,0:22:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I brought him back to life...\NThat monster... I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.70,0:22:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I brought him back to life...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:36.88,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And slowly, you come to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:44.30,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's all as it should be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.18,0:22:53.73,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You can only do so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.90,0:22:59.32,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If you're game enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:07.12,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You could place your trust in me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:16.21,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For the love of life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.34,0:23:21.55,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}There's a trade off
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.34,0:23:28.30,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We could lose it all
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:33.23,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But we'll go down fighting
